metadata.name: Eurby
metadata.description:
Eurby  (Er-Be) is the very first 1of1 of the Nostalgia 90s collection. In tribute to the famous "Furby". 
A lNostalgia brought to the blockchain to spread happiness and bring joyous memories.

Eurby was made using coloured pencils on black paper.
Dimensions: 2922 × 2922 pixels
